An expression of the form
=INLINEFT
(e‰1, e‰2)
=TEX
{} evaluates to a
pair, with first component and second component having respectively the values of
=INLINEFT
e‰1
=TEX
{} and 
=INLINEFT
e‰2
=TEX
. If
=INLINEFT
e‰1
=TEX
{} has type 
=INLINEFT
