	Square		nat ­ nat

	--- Types ---

	nat

	--- Fixity ---

	Infix 300:	pplus
	Infix 310:	ptimes

	--- Axioms ---

	P3		ô µ n· ³ zero = successor n
	P4		ô µ m n
			  · successor m = successor n ´ m = n
	P5		ô µ P
			  · P zero
			        ± (µ n· P n ´ P (successor n))
			      ´ (µ n· P n)
	pplus_def	ô (µ n· zero pplus n = n)
			    ± (µ m n
			    · successor m pplus n
